{"tid":1087972,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[非主流運動系列]【閃避球世界盃】港男隊邀請賽挫南非奪冠","createTime":"2019-04-01T16:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T17:23:58.000Z","uid":39206,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"db9d1cd58d3ed28528ae1e2da0d4d0e4754e493f","tid":1087972,"uid":39206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T16:45:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.sportsroad.hk/archives/209938\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportsroad.hk%2Farchives%2F209938&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQi8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=02b17584\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sportsroad.hk/archives/209938</a><br />\n【體路專訊】2018閃避球世界盃周五（3日）假紐約麥迪遜廣場花園開打，香港男子隊雖然未獲參賽資格，但獲邀出戰同場舉行的世界閃避球邀請賽，最終更擊敗南非取得冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n好似冇咩人提過，所以想攞出來講下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢幾年既香港運動員其實都幾出眾，無論係主流（單車，劍擊，羽毛球）定非主流（跳繩，閃避球），都有唔錯既成績，但就好似冇乜人知。<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都有玩過閃避球，我相信大部分人都係一玩就愛上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係點解大家都冇繼續玩落去，明明全世界都有人玩，原因就係冇人大力推廣（傳媒，政府）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港傳媒可唔可以大力d宣傳下</span></span></span>一d非主流而又出眾既運動，香港地方細而又唔係個個都中意玩足球同籃球，令到一d起其他運動領域度有潛能既人遇唔到岩自己既運動，間接抹殺左佢地既潛能。<br />\n<br />\n比多條片大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第二個玩法來<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Spu6OlAZHUo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSpu6OlAZHUo&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQi8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=cf91e192\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Spu6OlAZHUo</a><br />\n<br />\n可以見到真係鬥智鬥力   一d都不遜於主流運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n場地限制細同只要一個波就玩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多人 少人玩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw要讚下HK01 因為得佢有講呢件事"},{"pid":"746ecd9a9a3075e1aad0ddc21ac8a61959559685","tid":1087972,"uid":14983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:23:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\nbtw要讚下HK01 因為得佢有講呢件事</blockquote><br />\n不嬲紅底媒體報導本地體育都積極過啲所謂民主大報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}